            "product_text_content_1": "<p>Sportmediq’s idea was to create a very effective and long-lasting chalk that would be easy to apply without making a mess. This chalk has a consistency that feels like a lotion, and it dries in 15-25 seconds.</p><p>If you get liquid chalk, you expect it to come out of the bottle and into your palm without getting anywhere else. This, however, is not the case here because once you open the bottle, there’s a lot of chalk that comes out, and since there’s so much of it, it gets everywhere. The consistency is very nice, and it dries quickly, but the mess it makes is surprising and you don’t expect it from liquid chalk. Not to mention, the bottle gets messy too, because the chalk gets all over it, so it doesn’t stay looking clean for a long time. </p><p>Nevertheless, the grip it provides is really good and reliable, but it doesn’t last very long. You’ll need to reapply this after every set, and if your hands sweat a lot, you’ll have a hard time applying the chalk directly onto sweaty palms because it won’t stick. Make sure to pat your hands dry with a towel and then apply chalk. This way, you’ll have no issues with it sticking to your skin.</p>",
